features: 【Practical 6 Drawer Dresser】Six wider and larger drawers provide spacious storage space for your trivial sundries, meeting your storage needs in an all-round way. Traditional pulls have been replaced by gold metal pulls that can be pulled out and closed easily and silently. Stylish and simple. The back of the cabinet has cable management, ready to be used as a TV cabinet.

【Sturdy and stable】Our wood dresser has undergone rigorous testing. Made of MDF wood is scratch and wear resistant and water resistant. You can rest assured that it will last for years and provide solid stability. The fully wrapped wood panels also provide superior product quality. Our products are also water and scratch resistant, so you can use them with confidence for years to come.

Years of durability: Density board is the specially selected material to give the cabinet high density and strength, ensuring years of use. Robust metal rails ensure smooth drawer movement and removeable feet pads protect floors

Easy assembly & after-sale service: All hardware and clear instructions are included for a quick assembly; and we are committed to delivering fine items and service, any problem will be solved properly to your satisfaction

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Exactly like the photo
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. This was an easy build did it in a couple of hours. Looks exactly like the picture. The drawers pull out smoothly. When it’s all put together it’s quite light and easy to move around. The only difficulty was the screwing in you do have to use a bit of elbow grease but nothing to sweat over. Also it uses “cam lock fastening system” which can be frustrating to get to work but in the end it looks great and holds together so I’m very happy with the purchase

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice Finish, Build is Tough
reviews.reviewText: The finished product is very nice. The process of putting it together got frustrating at times. Building the center section is difficult, would recommend building with more than 1 person. Some of the pieces of the locking system were not long enough to secure. A few screws on the runners were hard to manually screw in which caused the drawers to catch and not close. This was fixed after a few tries, but made the assembly process longer.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to Build
reviews.reviewText: The shipment was fast, all parts were there and in excellent condition. The building instructions were complete m, simple and easy to follow. The construction was one-person easy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars difficult but possible
reviews.reviewText: The end result is very cute, but the process is very long/frustrating. It’s not a problem with the instructions, which are very easy to follow, but rather the construction of the dresser. The pre drilled holes don’t completely line up sometimes, and some screws don’t quite reach long enough to keep it as sturdy as it could be down the middle. It’s nice for now, but I don’t see it holding up for more than a couple of years.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Took 3 hours with 2 people
reviews.reviewText: Instructions are ok. Just have to look at each step a few times to make sure I’m working in the same direction as the pics. The most frustrating part is building the center section. But in the end it comes together and becomes a solid piece. Wife and I put it together, maybe that’s why it took 3 hours….lol

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I love the look of this dresser; it goes perfectly with my bedroom decor. The only thing is a few of the drawers stick and I have to shake them a bit to open and close them. But that could be due to my handiworks of putting them together.
